Project tutorial:

In this project, there are 6 files. The blackjack environment class is in blackjack.py.
This class uses classes from the player.py and statcollector.py to run the game. The util.py file contained
helper methods, enums, as well as a method and class taken from the Berkley pacman reinforcement
learning project. Besides these two small items, the rest of the project is original and my own work.
Finally, there is a file blackjack-tests.py, this file contains unit tests that were used to ensure the
blackjack environment’s correctness during development. This file has no other purpose in terms of the
project or the research but main be run using “python blackjack-tests.py”.

The main project script is call project-script.py. This file takes in command line arguments in order
to define the characteristics of the game. Each experiment was run by altering the command line arguments
to create the appropriate rules. Each command line has a default option and therefore the script can be
run by typing “python project-script.py” in the command line and pressing enter.

Some example command line entries are below:

python project-script.py

python project-script.py --win-reward=1 --lose-reward=-1 --alpha =0.5 --discount=0.5 --epsilon=0.5 --epsilonDecreasing=False

python project-script.py --win-reward=1 --lose-reward=-1 --alpha=0.1 --discount=0.25 --epsilon=0.25

python project-script.py --win-reward=1 --lose-reward=-1 --alpha=0.9 --discount=0.9 --epsilon=0.9

 python project-script.py --win-reward=5 --push-reward=-2 --lose-reward=-5 --alpha=0.7 --discount=0.5 --epsilon=0.25

python project-script.py --win-reward=1 --lose-reward=-1 --alpha=0.1 --discount=0.25 --epsilon=1 --epsilonDecreasing=True

python project-script.py --win-reward=5 --lose-reward=-10 --alpha=0.1 --discount=0.25 --epsilon=0.5 --epsilonDecreasing=True


python project-script.py --win-reward=5 --lose-reward=-5 --alpha=0.1 --discount=0.25 --epsilon=0.25 --epsilonDecreasing=True --epsilonDecreasingFactor=0.025

python project-script.py --win-reward=5 --lose-reward=-5 --alpha=0.1 --discount=0.25 --epsilon=0.5 --epsilonDecreasing=True --epsilonDecreasingFactor=0.05


python project-script.py --win-reward=5 --lose-reward=-5 --alpha=0.1 --discount=0.5 --epsilon=0.5 --epsilonDecreasing=True —epsilonDecreasingFactor=0.05

python project-script.py --win-reward=5 --lose-reward=-5 --alpha=0.1 --discount=0.25 --epsilon=0.25 --epsilonDecreasing=True --epsilonDecreasingFactor=0.025 —collapsedStateSpace=True

python project-script.py --win-reward=5 --lose-reward=-5 --alpha=0.1 --discount=0.25 --epsilon=0.25 --epsilonDecreasing=True --epsilonDecreasingFactor=0.025 --qLearningBetting=True

